<div class=3D"WordSection1">
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-se=
rif">Good morning Rafaella,<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-se=
rif">As per the next phase of the process map &#8211; Stephen Walker from A=
SURNZ &#8211; our Technical Building Consultant is due to visit site and au=
thor the scope of works required.
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-se=
rif">Stephen and I will be visiting site at
<u>12:30 today</u> to complete the walk-through and determine the scope-of-=
works for the repairs to your home.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-se=
rif">Once we have completed this document &#8211; I can return and go throu=
gh each item on the scope line-by-line in detail with you so you can gain t=
he confidence that we have captured everything.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-se=
rif">When we go through the scope together &#8211; we can consider adding a=
nything further that is necessary if we need to. I am exceptionally confide=
nt that Stephen and I will capture everything on the
 first draft &#8211; but I want you to know that you will sign-off on the s=
cope-of-works as being complete before we move to the repair phase.<o:p></o=
:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-se=
rif">You do not need to join us for today&#8217;s visit &#8211; but you are=
 more than welcome to if you wish. As I stated &#8211; we can review it tog=
ether once complete. I will let you decide whether you wish to join
 us or not.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-se=
rif">Please do not hesitate to contact me if you have any questions or conc=
erns at all.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-se=
rif">Many Thanks,<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-se=
rif">Grant. <o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-se=
rif"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
